
---

## 🛠️ How to Use

1. Clone or download this repo
2. Open `Sentiment_Dashboard.pbix` in Power BI Desktop
3. Use filters to explore sentiment patterns across time and topic
4. Replace the dataset in `/data` with your own CSV to update visuals

---

## 🔍 Use Cases

- 🌐 Social media campaign analysis  
- 🗳️ Political sentiment tracking during elections  
- 🏢 Brand reputation monitoring  
- 🎥 Movie or event feedback analysis  
- 📈 Market reaction during product launches or crises

